  requiresDecision: 1
  decisionKey: governance-approach
  decisionTitle: DRAIN WORK KA RAASTA
  decisionMessage: Monsoon paas hai. Open tender slower but auditable hai; ek verbal
    contractor fast completion promise karta hai, bina complete cost sheet ke.
  firstOption: 'OPEN E-TENDER

    Delivery +8 / Integrity +12'
  secondOption: 'VERBAL SHORTCUT

    Delivery +14 / Integrity -15'
  secondDialogue: Verbal contractor kaam tez karta hai, par final bill estimate se
    Rs 3 lakh zyada aur measurement trail incomplete nikalta hai.
